Matt. xxvi. 21-^25, and parallel places in the other 
Evangelists. 

2. Many events have been foretold by God, which are 
consequent and dependent on the moral conduct of par* 
ticttlar persons, and were accomplished either by their 
virtuous or vicious actions. Thus, the children of Israel's 
