4. Unless God foreknows the future acts of moral 
agents, all the prophecies we have in Scripture concern- 
ing the great antichristian apostasy ; the rise, reign, wick* 
ed qualities, and deeds, of the man of sin, and his instru- 
ments and adherents ; the extent and long continuance of 
