in the street. — He shall bring forth judgment unto truth. 
He shall not fail nor be discouraged, till he have set judg- 
ment in the earth ; and the isles shall wait for his law.^ 
This promise, of Christ's having God's Spirit put upon 
him, and his not crying and lifting up his voice, etc. re- 
