And yet the same Dr. Whitby asserts, that fallen man 
is not able to perform perfect obedience. In p. 165, he 
has these words : <' The nature of Adam had power to 
continue innocent and without sin ; whereas it is certain 
our nature never had." But if we ha%'e not power to 
