art few Arminiao divines, who, if ihoroagbljr tried, would 
stand to these principles. They will allow, that God is, 
in the highest sense, an active being, and the highest 
fountain of life and action ; and tliey would not probably 
deny, that those that are called God's acts of righteous-- 
